        <Meaning id="c92ebef8-44e6-425d-a5bd-96dbf14d1aec" type="Proper Noun">
          <Vi>Aaron</Vi>
          <En>A biblical figure; the elder brother of Moses and the first High Priest of the Israelites.</En>
          <Example>Moses and Aaron led the Israelites out of Egypt according to the Book of Exodus.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
